<div class="container my-5">
  <div class="text-center mb-4">
    <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold">Welcome to <span class="text-primary">Whats New!!</span></h1>
    <h2 class="lead">The new messaging app made for everyone</h2>
  </div>

  <div class="row justify-content-center">
    <div class="col-md-10">
      <div class="card shadow-sm">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h4 class="card-title text-center mb-3"><i class="bi bi-chat-dots-fill"></i> How to Use Whats New</h4>
          <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
            <li class="list-group-item">
              <strong>Step 1:</strong> Log in or sign up to unlock full access to chats and messages. Without logging in, you can only view the users list.
            </li>
            <li class="list-group-item">
              <strong>Step 2:</strong> To start a conversation, head to the <strong>Chats</strong> section in the navbar and click <em>New Chat</em>.
            </li>
            <li class="list-group-item">
              <strong>Step 3:</strong> Choose the person you want to chat with when creating a chat.
            </li>
            <li class="list-group-item">
              <strong>Step 4:</strong> Go to the <strong>Messages</strong> tab and click <em>New Message</em> to send your first message.
            </li>
            <li class="list-group-item">
              <strong>Step 5:</strong> Ensure you select the correct chat when sending a message.
            </li>
            <li class="list-group-item">
              <strong>Step 6:</strong> Visit the <strong>Users</strong> tab to view or edit your profile and see all the chats you're in.
            </li>
          </ul>
          <div class="text-center mt-4">
            <p class="mb-1">Feel free to explore all the sections through the navigation bar!</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
